<section class="hero"><div class="wrap hero-grid"><div class="hero-copy"><div class="eyebrow">Premium cleaning services</div><h1>Beautiful results with a <span>professional cleaning company</span> you can trust.</h1><p class="lead">Carpet cleaning, upholstery cleaning, stain removal and specialist care for homes and businesses that want a cleaner, fresher, more professional finish.</p><div class="hero-actions"><a class="button button-primary" href="contact.html">Request a quote</a><a class="button button-light" href="services.html">View services</a></div><div class="trust-row"><div><strong>Trusted</strong>friendly and reliable service</div><div><strong>Professional</strong>powerful equipment and methods</div><div><strong>Tailored</strong>domestic and commercial work</div></div></div><aside class="form-card"><h3>Get a fast quote</h3><p>Tell us what you need and we will get back to you.</p><div class="field"><label>Name</label><input placeholder="Your name"></div><div class="field"><label>Phone</label><input placeholder="Your number"></div><div class="field"><label>Service</label><select><option>Carpet cleaning</option><option>Upholstery cleaning</option><option>Stain removal</option><option>Commercial cleaning</option></select></div><div class="field"><label>Message</label><textarea placeholder="Tell us about the areas to be cleaned"></textarea></div><a class="button button-dark" href="contact.html">Send enquiry</a></aside></div></section>
<section><div class="wrap"><div class="section-head"><div><h2>Our services</h2></div><p>Original content and layout designed to give you a strong local cleaning company website structure, without copying another business page.</p></div><div class="grid-4"><article class="card"><div class="icon">01</div><h3>Carpet cleaning</h3><p>Deep cleaning for domestic and commercial carpets with a cleaner, fresher finish.</p></article><article class="card"><div class="icon">02</div><h3>Upholstery cleaning</h3><p>Sofas, chairs and fabric furnishings cleaned with care and attention.</p></article><article class="card"><div class="icon">03</div><h3>Stain treatment</h3><p>Targeted spotting and fibre safe treatment for common and stubborn marks.</p></article><article class="card"><div class="icon">04</div><h3>Commercial work</h3><p>Reliable service for offices, communal areas, rental properties and more.</p></article></div></div></section>
<section><div class="wrap split"><div class="dark-panel panel"><div class="eyebrow" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);color:#fff">Why choose us</div><h2 style="margin:0 0 12px">A stronger, more premium impression from the first glance.</h2><p>We focus on a clean, trustworthy service and clear communication from first enquiry to finished result.</p><ul class="list"><li>Professional presentation and customer care</li><li>Tailored solutions for homes and businesses</li><li>Reliable booking and honest advice</li><li>Attention to detail on every job</li></ul></div><div class="panel card"><div class="section-head" style="display:block;margin-bottom:12px"><h2 style="font-size:34px">Areas we cover</h2><p style="margin-top:10px">Serving Ludlow, Shrewsbury, Hereford and surrounding areas.</p></div><div class="table-like"><div><span>Shrewsbury</span><span>Domestic and commercial</span></div><div><span>Ludlow</span><span>Domestic and specialist work</span></div><div><span>Hereford</span><span>Homes and businesses</span></div><div><span>Surrounding areas</span><span>Please ask</span></div></div></div></div></section>
